INSERT INTO C_Tax_Acct (C_Tax_ID, C_AcctSchema_ID, AD_Client_ID, AD_Org_ID, IsActive, Created, CreatedBy, Updated, UpdatedBy, T_Due_Acct, T_Liability_Acct, T_Credit_Acct, T_Receivables_Acct, T_Expense_Acct) SELECT t.C_Tax_ID, s.C_Acctschema_ID, t.AD_Client_ID, t.AD_Org_ID, t.IsActive, t.Created, t.CreatedBy, t.Updated, t.UpdatedBy, ad.T_Due_Acct, ad.T_Liability_Acct, ad.T_Credit_Acct, ad.T_Receivables_Acct, ad.T_Expense_Acct FROM C_Tax t, C_AcctSchema s, C_AcctSchema_Default ad WHERE ad.C_AcctSchema_ID = s.C_AcctSchema_ID AND s.AD_Client_ID = t.AD_Client_ID AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM C_Tax_Acct WHERE C_Tax_Acct.C_Tax_ID = t.C_Tax_ID)
